{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486760/extras/crocosAnimGif.gif?t=1727511421\" />Crocogame is a fast-paced roguelite game with rewarding difficulty progression. The player controls cute crocos, with unique stats and ultimate spells in order to defeat deadly enemies on various challenging maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAME FOCUS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is balanced around intense moment-to-moment combat, where movement and attack resources must be used efficiently to achieve victory. A big part of the game's progression revolves around stackable difficulty modifiers, which can turn every map harder in exchange for new, cool rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHARACTER CUSTOMISATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During gameplay, the player upgrades impactful stats and collects gameplay-altering essences. As the difficulty modifiers stack up, more essence slots are unlocked, leading to unique build combinations with unexpected synergies and explosive results.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486760/extras/essenceSlideNew.gif?t=1727511421\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Fast runs (~15 minutes each).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 10 build-defining stats you can upgrade every time you level up.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 6 unique crocos with diverse base stats and ultimate spells.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 70+ powerful essences with gameplay-altering effects. You can combine up to 4 of them to create unique builds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 3 playable maps with different challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 10 difficulty modifiers for each map to put your skills to the test.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Achievement-based progression. Unlock new crocos, essences, maps and difficulty points by completing achievements on different difficulty levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Challenging normal and elite enemies with diverse movesets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Twin-stick controls for complete immersion in the action.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you climb to the top and complete all the maps at the highest difficulty level?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486760/extras/crocoGifHigher.gif?t=1727511421\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Sewers domination","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2486760/5e5f2eb9b0d7432d265395d38a0aabb97c023234.jpg"},{"name":"Ruins domination","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2486760/ee8ab248d50fbf1c7ac7fcd7a15ac4915c00f548.jpg"},{"name":"Crypt domination","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2486760/038647000a10574f0d4d07a5a73fd6bab2bc376b.jpg"},{"name":"Elusive croco","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2486760/b75db115cd714ac417c51ff5e41315ec094e0644.jpg"},{"name":"Crocos assemble","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2486760/19b2fc7d127f927addcc62126608ccaf160eed9e.jpg"},{"name":"Difficulty 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2486760/291ac9fa49939568ff9eec350d02b136837006d1.jpg"},{"name":"Difficulty 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2486760/59eaad79ef89c1a5a83525cfd8516f628d497960.jpg"},{"name":"Difficulty 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam